title: Deprivation, United Kingdom, 2007
name: Deprivation, United Kingdom, 2007
description: Association of Public Health Observatories publishes data on the Level of deprivation of a population in an area, as measured by the percentage of people in that area living in the most deprived fifth of areas in England. The differences in deprivation between areas are a major determinant of health inequality in the United Kingdom.
